<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> cīrkoṇṭa veḷḷāṟu kurutip perukkiṟa
<lb n="2"/>cevvāṟu paṭṭoṭa vavvāṟu ceṉṟap por veṉ
</p>

<p>1. Read <hi rend="grantha">sahasra</hi></p> 

<p>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṟu vaṉpey naṭaṅkaṇṭataṟpiṉ puliyūr naṭaṅkaṇ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭa puvanekavirar pār paṇṭaḷantuṇṭorāliṟ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>kkum <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> rai<unclear>ppata</unclear>ṅ koṇṭa Ila pa<hi rend="grantha">tma</hi>nāpar kārkoṇṭa
<lb n="6"/>niṉkaiyil velukku vaṟṟuṅkaṭalalla veṉpetai kaṇ
<lb n="7"/>ṭā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kaṭale § māṟupaṭum maṉṉavar taṅkai pūṇṭavāḷi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rumpu ve <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> mavar kāl pūṇṭu viṭṭate ciṟimiku veṭṭantiri
<lb n="9"/>kaḷiṟṟu vikkiramapāṇṭiyaṉ taṉāṭṭaṅ kaṭai civanta nāḷ [§*]
